[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "あ、来たわね。こっちよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00079",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "ヤンネさん、連れて来たよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00080",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ええっと……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00081",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "こちらのお方は？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00082",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "はじめまして。私はクレオ・ランターナ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00083",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "苗字と、国の名前が同じ……お姫様？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00084",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "うん。ランターナ王国の王女だよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00085",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "わ、私はノーヴァ神聖国の案内人、\nアルビーナ・ジムロックと申します！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00086",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "あはは、そんな固くならないでよ。最近は隊を率いて\n南方辺境にいたから、その態度はむず痒いかも",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00087",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "現場に長くいると、色々と雑になりますものね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00088",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "い、いや、しかし、辺境というと戦いの最前線では？\n王女様が陣頭に立たれるなんて……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00089",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "私は確かに王族だけど、それ以前に武芸の才能が\nあるから。国の政にはオルペウス兄さんがいるし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00090",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "それと、まぁ、リヒャルト兄さんもいるから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00091",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "リヒャルト兄さん、なんか扱いが雑っすね……\nっていうか、リヒャルトって確か……ロマンさん？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00092",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "リヒャルト兄さんのこと知ってるの？\nさすが兄さん、顔が広いんだね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00093",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "お兄様には、かねがね、お世話に……\nなったような、お世話をしたような",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00094",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ちょ、ちょっとベップ！　不敬！　不敬だから！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00095",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "いいよ。だってリヒャルト兄さんだし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00096",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "は、はあ、そっすか……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00097",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "アルビーナとベップちゃんを呼んだ理由なんだけど、\nクレオ様がヘルトについて知りたいそうなのよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00098",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "あ、呼び捨てとかちゃん付けでいいよ。\n様付けは堅苦しくて慣れないもん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00099",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（いや、王女様にちゃん付けは、さすがに……\n　王族とは思えぬ距離の詰め方だなぁ）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00100",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "……それで、ヘルトなんだけど……\nどこへ行ったか、知らない？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00101",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ああ、それなら知ってますよ。雷鳴の島です。\nレスナたちがそこで戦うって昨日旅立ちました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00102",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "は？　戦う……？　昨日旅立った……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00103",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "はい。ここで待ってたら、\nそのうち会えると思いますよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00104",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "レスナたちが倒して、捕まえて戻って来るはず――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00105",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "戻って来るのを、待つ？\nそんな悠長なことしてられない――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00106",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "雷鳴の島の詳しい場所を教えて。\n私もそこへ向かう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00107",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "え、まさか今から追いかける気ですか？\n危ないし、間に合わないすよ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00108",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "間に合う間に合わないの問題じゃないんだ。\nヘルトには、借りがあるの……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00109",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "借り、ですか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00110",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "うん。私が結成した特殊部隊……「光星隊」が、\nあいつとゼロって女に壊滅させられたんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00111",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "クレオ・ランターナ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo Lantarna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "高貴な雰囲気を纏う女性。\nとある目的のため、ノーヴァ神聖国を訪れている",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]